title: Opinion: How the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services became the shining light of Trump’s second term
description: There is plenty of bad coming out of the federal government on health care. CMS is the exception, write Ezekiel J. Emanuel and Merjan L. Ozisik.
content: There is plenty of bad coming out of the federal government on health care. CMS is the exception, write Ezekiel J. Emanuel and Merjan L. Ozisik.
